// 1. Replaced "var" with "Holder storage" in functions Put and Collect to explicitly specify storage location of struct variable.
// 2. Added a require statement in function Collect to check if the balance is sufficient and the unlock time has been reached.
// 3. Replaced the external call in function Collect with a transfer statement to prevent reentrancy vulnerability.
